Package: PAGe
Type: Package
Title: Phase-Aligned Gated Epidemic Forecasting
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Lennon", "Li", email = "lennon.li@oahpp.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://lennon-li.github.io/PAGe/, https://github.com/lennon-li/PAGe
BugReports: https://github.com/lennon-li/PAGe/issues
Description: Prospective one- and two-week-ahead forecasts of seasonal
  respiratory-virus positivity. A gated pipeline detects epidemic ignition,
  aligns partial seasons to historical reference curves, and produces binomial
  generalized additive model forecasts with adaptive bias correction. Training
  and evaluation support leakage-safe leave-one-season-out validation,
  prior-informed tuning, candidate racing, and explicit promotion gates.
